==Trivia==
* {{p|Mewtwo}} is currently the only [[Legendary Pokémon]] in {{g|GO}} to have an event-exclusive form.
** Armored Mewtwo is also the only event-exclusive form in the game to have different base stats from its normal form, being more defense-weighted than regular Mewtwo.
* {{p|Lugia}} caught at GO Fest 2017 in Chicago and {{p|Mewtwo}} caught at Pokémon GO Stadium in Yokohama appear when searching "Costume" in the list of a player's caught Pokémon. They do not appear in the Event Pokédex.

